description:
Mother`s been defeated, and the protagonist flees from Ariel into Keren County. But unexpected guests keep arriving, one after another. One of them is from the Kingdom of Ohts, and is after her power. The other is the adminstrator, Güliedistodiez.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: C`est quand même pas ma faute, si ?
This Isn`t My Fault, Is It?
Watashi no Sei ja Nai, yo ne?
私のせいじゃない, よね?
